# FlowOS — Sprint 2.1: Schema Foundations

## Status — Completed 20 July 2026

Sprint 2.1 has been completed on the `Phase-2` branch.

Delivered:
- Added the `SOURCE`, `CREATE`, `UPDATE`, and `DELETE` A1 data-node schema coverage, including explicit connector binding through `SOURCE`.
